# TC_01 – Bank transfer between own accounts (valid scenario)

## Preconditions:
- User is logged in to the mobile banking app
- User has at least 2 active accounts

## Test Steps:
1. Open banking app
2. Go to "Transfers"
3. Select "Between own accounts"
4. Choose source account
5. Choose destination account
6. Enter amount (e.g. 100 PLN)
7. Tap "Confirm"

## Expected Result:
- Transfer is successfully completed
- Balance is updated in both accounts
- Confirmation message is displayed
- Transaction appears in history